{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a criminal offence to take direct pictures of other people\u2019s children",
        "additional_details": "If they are standing in a public place, anyone can have the right to take the pictures of your children, even in your own back garden. We think it\u2019s disgusting and it\u2019s wrong and could help to protect predators. Let's start protecting every child instead.",
        "background": "It shouldn\u2019t matter if it\u2019s in a shopping centre in a park or on the bus please make it a criminal offence to take direct pictures of other people\u2019s children without consent.",
